cf3 Jer_16:18\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Jer_32:34\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_12:11\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 2Th_2:3-4\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298  \par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b NOTAS\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\par\par 24:15 Al parecer, Daniel designaba con ello un altar pagano que Ant\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 oco Ep\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 fanes erigi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  en el Templo de Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n (el 168: ver \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 1Ma_1:54\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). La aplicaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n evang\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 lica se realiz\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  cuando la Ciudad Santa y su Templo fueron sitiados y luego ocupados por los ej\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 rcitos paganos de Roma, ver \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Luk_21:20\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 . \par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang0\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang0\langnp0\langfe0\langfenp0\b CTGNT-Robertson:\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298  \par Una alusi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n a \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_12:11\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 . Ant\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 oco Epifanes erigi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  un altar a Zeus sobre el altar a Jehov\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 1Ma_1:54\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 1Ma_1:59\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 1Ma_6:7\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 2Ma_6:1-5\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). La desolaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n en la mente de Jes\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'fa\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s es aparentemente el ej\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 rcito romano (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Luk_21:20\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ) en el templo, una aplicaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n de las palabras de Daniel a este temido acontecimiento. El verbo bdelussomai significa sentir n\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 usea debido al hedor, aborrecer, detestar. La idolatr\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 a era un hedor para Dios (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Luk_16:15\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Rev_17:4\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). Josefo relata que los romanos quemaron el templo y ofrecieron sacrificios a sus ense\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 as, situadas en la puerta oriental, cuando proclamaron emperador a Tito.l\par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b CB-Beacon\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 : \par Esta expresi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n significa \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'93\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 la abominaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n que trae desolamiento\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'94\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  (cf. \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_12:11\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ), Arndt y Gingrich la definen \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'93\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 como algo detestable que causar\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  la desolaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n del lugar santo\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'94\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 . [[Op. cit., p. 137.]]\par\par Est\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  identificada con lo que habl\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  el profeta Daniel (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Mat_24:15\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). Aparece tres veces en Daniel (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_12:11\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ) y tambi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n se halla en \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 1Ma_1:54\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298  donde aparentemente se la emplea para denotar el altar de Zeus levantado sobre el altar sagrado en el templo en 168 a.c. Daniel parece referirse a la misma cosa. Aqu\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  hay una doble alusi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n: al a\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 o 70 a.c. y al final de la edad.\par\par La frase s\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 lo se encuentra en el Nuevo Testamento en el pasaje paralelo \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Mar_13:14\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 . Para esta enigm\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 tica expresi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n apocal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 ptica Lucas (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Luk_21:20\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ) tiene una llana declaraci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n para sus lectores gentiles\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'97\'93\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 cuando viereis a Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n rodeada de ej\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 rcitos\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'94\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 . La abominaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n podr\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 a ser entonces las \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 guilas romanas sobre los estandartes de los soldados del sitio. En el margen de \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298  se lee: \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'93\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Sobre las murallas estar\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n los \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 dolos del desolador.\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'94\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  La masacre de los zelotes a sus compa\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 eros jud\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 os durante el asedio puede ser otra aplicaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n, puesto que ellos profanaron el templo. Dado que los tres Sin\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 pticos urgen a los creyentes a huir a las monta\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 as, parece que se refieren al mismo acontecimiento. Pero eso no significa que no haya aqu\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  tambi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n una aplicaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n sobre el establecimiento de la imagen del anticristo en Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n, al final de esta edad (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Rev_13:14\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ).\par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b BE-DV\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 :\par\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'bf\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 Qu\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  es esta \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ab\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 abominaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n desoladora\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'bb\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  que Daniel y Jes\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'fa\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s mencionan? Antes que como un objeto espec\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 fico, acontecimiento o persona, pudiera interpretarse como un intento deliberado de mofarse y negar la realidad de la presencia de Dios. La predicci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n de Daniel se hizo realidad en 168 a.C. cuando Ant\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 oco Ep\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 fanes sacrific\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  un cerdo a Zeus en el altar del templo santo (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:30\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 , \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). Las palabras de Jes\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'fa\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s resonaron en 70 d.C., cuando Tito coloc\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  un \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 dolo en el lugar del templo incendiado despu\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s de destruir Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n. Al final de los tiempos, el Anticristo levantar\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  una estatua de s\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  mismo y ordenar\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  que todos la adoren (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 2Th_2:4\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Rev_13:14\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 , \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Rev_13:15\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). Estas son todas las \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ab\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 abominaciones\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'bb\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  que buscar\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n desacreditar lo santo.\par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b BE-MacArthur\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 :\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b abominaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n desoladora\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 . Vea las notas sobre \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_9:27\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298  ; \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Dan_11:31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 . Esta frase, referida originalmente a la profanaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n del templo por Antioco Ep\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 fanes, rey de Siria en la segunda centuria a.C. Antioco invadi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n en el a\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 o 168 a.C., transform\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  el altar en un santuario para Zeus, e incluso sacrific\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  cerdos en \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 l. Sin embargo, Jes\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'fa\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s claramente estaba viendo hacia una futura "abominaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n desoladora". Algunos sugieren que esta profec\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'ed\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 a fue cumplida en el a\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 o 70 d.C. cuando Tito invadi\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  Jerusal\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n y destruy\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  el templo vea la nota sobre el v. \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Mat_24:2\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ). Sin embargo, el ap\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 stol Pablo vio un cumplimiento a\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'fa\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n futuro (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 2Th_2:3-4\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ) al igual que Juan (\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Rev_13:14-15\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ) cuando el anticristo coloque una imagen en el templo durante la futura tribulaci\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f3\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 n. Las palabras de Cristo, por consiguiente, van m\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 s all\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  del a\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'f1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 o 70 d.C. a una \loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e9\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2 poca de cataclismo aun mayor que preceder\loch\af2\dbch\af2\hich\f2\'e1\hich\af2\dbch\af2\loch\f2  inmediatamente su venida (cp. vv. \plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ai\aul\acf3\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\i\ul\cf3 Mat_24:29-31\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298 ).\par\par\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ab\ltrch\f2\fs24\lang12298\langnp12298\langfe12298\langfenp12298\b LBLA\plain\rtlch\af2\afs24\alang12298\ltrch\f2\fs24